sequenceDiagram
    actor Player
    participant System
    
    Note over Player, System: UC-03: Move Hero
    Player->>System: pressArrowKey(direction)
    System->>System: calculateTargetCell(direction)
    System->>System: checkCollision()
    
    alt Has sufficient Energy and cell is free
        System->>System: deductEnergy(moveCost)
        System-->>Player: updateHeroPositionAndStats()
    else Lacks sufficient Energy
        System-->>Player: play error sound
        System-->>Player: Hero remains in place
    end